{"tid":568671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保證不再外遇又和女學生拍性愛片！　偷情夫簽承諾書還是忍不住","createTime":"2018-02-22T04:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T09:49:46.000Z","uid":74796,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5cff19afd68ecfa2f3bd97566d5d6c1c807a67","tid":568671,"uid":74796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"桃園一名男子2010年和同為舞蹈老師的施姓妻子結婚，婚後育有1男1女，但是卻在2013年和蕭姓女子發生婚外情，當時被妻子原諒，同時答應簽下「承諾書」發誓不再偷吃，否則就將繳清房貸，並將房產、小孩監護權都歸給老婆；不料，該名男子2015年又和女學生譜出戀曲，但最後只願意離婚，不願移轉房屋所有權。桃園地院判准離婚，但是房產轉移、繳清房貸違反善良風俗，不必移轉。<br />\n<br />\n該名男子立下承諾書後，約定若再有外遇，願意無條件辦理離婚，且願將環北路房地過戶給妻子，並將房屋貸款繳清，還必須將子與監護權讓給女方，沒想到不到大約2年的時間，再次發生婚外情。<br />\n<br />\n施女表示，2016年11月間在整理家中物品時，無意間<span style=\"color: red;\">發現丈夫與女學生的性愛影片</span>，經質問之下才發覺，老公和學生從2015年5、6月就開始交往了，對此受到極大的打擊，分別對2人提出妨害家庭告訴。<br />\n<br />\n法官認為，兩人的婚姻之所以會破裂，是因為該名男子履次與女性有不正當的交往關係，無視婚姻、家庭的圓滿及經營，甚至還和兩人的學生拍性愛影片，使女方及年幼子女天倫夢碎，還導致施女精神飽受折磨，因此判准離婚，還判男子必須賠償妻子40萬元的慰撫金；至於付清房貸、轉移房產一事，法官提到，「預為離婚及賠償」的約定違背善良風俗，判不必移轉。"},{"pid":"22e0f51d903bf65c362d67c895a680d257942334","tid":568671,"uid":127123,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"好明顯老婆請女學生勾引佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb749ee95f216d4f7ec5ef7724481a3b0793971","tid":568671,"uid":171520,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T04:24:33.000Z","msg":"咩野係「違反善良風俗」?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁簽份承諾書即係廢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab41afc514a55ba1c63760cdcecd1eb67d6fcb7","tid":568671,"uid":10568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"所以咪話"},{"pid":"3d1d0a01eaf62e3df9f7c468130e633d49912aa1","tid":568671,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但是房產轉移、繳清房貸違反善良風俗，不必移轉。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b496c423f101a745bf94ca37d592562945b83034","tid":568671,"uid":49483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"台灣法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14723c3db62ff8d89902128fb39acc97e9f8c8ce","tid":568671,"uid":57488,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"乜嘢叫「善良風俗」<br />\n台灣啲法律好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699f0bae28490bc66f9b368b2f6df610aa289dcd","tid":568671,"uid":123605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"咁正<br />\n食完學生妹離婚唔洗分身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678d6c27a18d267328314c6a60e7fc731ce2e41b","tid":568671,"uid":53554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T04:52:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4ed5e85cdffa9c63c416f77444deb5abd15b473","tid":568671,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/2-16-2018/VoDACH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F2-16-2018%2FVoDACH.gif&h=6d063292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入球球員🇭🇰劉智樂(標準流浪)<br />\n2018-02-25 14:30 陽光元朗 vs 標準流浪 港超 元朗大球場 $60,$20"},{"pid":"c413ce9d3597d5f6d6bceab6bff2589b952ba784","tid":568671,"uid":5749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"桃園goallllllll<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f68d414e47f23ab158df4b23dd6ac38b707ed3","tid":568671,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"台灣有邊日係無風化新聞"},{"pid":"7fa8e4df5afd124541640e444d203afc2b9f5b31","tid":5686